query:
SELECT DISTINCT uc.name as categoryName 
FROM sites s
JOIN shopping_centres sc ON s.centreId = sc.id
JOIN site_usage_categories suc ON s.id = suc.siteId
JOIN usage_categories uc ON suc.categoryId = uc.id
WHERE sc.name LIKE '%Chullora%'
ORDER BY uc.name;
